text: what's up guys I am back home in Bangkok
and I've been planning the rest of my
travels in 2019 to hopefully finish all
the countries in the world by December I
just booked flights to visit the nine
remaining countries in the Pacific
Islands in February then I just have 19
left in Africa five in Latin America and
seven in the Middle East it's giving me
butterflies in my stomach to think that
I'll be able to say that I've been to
every single country in the world my
lifelong goal is inching closer and it's
gonna be a wild deer ahead but one of my
biggest goals this year is to get to
know all of you better so if you could
please comment below and tell me your
name where you're from and tell me what
are you up to in life bonus points if
you include a photo of yourself and
double bonus points if you add a short
10-second video clip I will be staying
up all night reading and watching your
stories so please don't be a stranger
I'm driven ski and if you like my travel
videos please click Subscribe and join
me as I plan to visit every country in
the world
